<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Brownson Industrial Consulting Brochure</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Brownson Industrial Consulting brochure — conveyor system recovery, downtime reduction, and maintenance reliability support.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root{
      --navy:#0c1f3f;
      --navy-2:#09162c;
      --blue:#345d94;
      --orange:#f57c00;
      --light:#f4f6fb;
      --text:#1c2b4a;
      --muted:#5f6f8a;
      --white:#ffffff;
      --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
      --radius:16px;
    }

    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
      font-family:Inter,sans-serif;
    }

    body{
      background:var(--light);
      color:var(--text);
      padding:34px;
    }

    .brochure{
      max-width:1050px;
      margin:auto;
      background:#fff;
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero{
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(12,31,63,.80), rgba(12,31,63,.82)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565008447742-97f6f38c985c?q=80&w=1800&auto=format&fit=crop");
      background-size:cover;
      background-position:center;
      color:#fff;
      padding:90px 55px;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-block;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
      padding:8px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      font-size:13px;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:.3px;
    }

    .hero h1{
      font-size:46px;
      margin-bottom:12px;
      line-height:1.12;
    }

    .hero p{
      font-size:18px;
      max-width:760px;
      line-height:1.8;
      color:#ecf2ff;
    }

    .content{
      padding:55px;
    }

    .section{
      margin-bottom:42px;
    }

    .section h2{
      font-size:30px;
      margin-bottom:16px;
      border-left:5px solid var(--orange);
      padding-left:14px;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .section p{
      font-size:17px;
      line-height:1.9;
      margin-bottom:15px;
      color:#30415e;
    }

    .bullets{
      display:grid;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:12px;
    }

    .bullet{
      background:#f7f9fd;
      border:1px solid #e6edf7;
      padding:14px 16px;
      border-radius:12px;
      font-weight:600;
      color:#30415e;
    }

    .stats{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:20px;
      margin-top:20px;
    }

    .stat{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),#173766);
      color:#fff;
      padding:34px 24px;
      border-radius:16px;
      text-align:center;
      box-shadow:0 12px 26px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
    }

    .stat h3{
      font-size:36px;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .stat p{
      color:#dce6f7;
      font-size:15px;
      margin:0;
    }

    .cta{
      background:linear-gradient(to right,var(--navy),var(--blue));
      color:#fff;
      padding:46px 55px;
      text-align:center;
    }

    .cta h2{
      margin-bottom:12px;
      font-size:32px;
    }

    .cta p{
      font-size:17px;
      margin-bottom:22px;
      color:#eaf0fb;
      line-height:1.8;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-block;
      background:var(--orange);
      color:#fff;
      text-decoration:none;
      padding:14px 28px;
      border-radius:10px;
      font-weight:800;
      box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(245,124,0,.24);
    }

    .footer{
      text-align:center;
      padding:26px;
      font-size:14px;
      color:#6a7892;
      background:#f8f9fc;
      line-height:1.8;
    }

    @media(max-width:900px){
      .stats{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .hero h1{
        font-size:34px;
      }

      .content,.hero,.cta{
        padding:30px 24px;
      }

      body{
        padding:14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="brochure">
    <div class="hero">
      <span class="eyebrow">Case Study • Conveyor Reliability • Downtime Reduction</span>
      <h1>Conveyor System Recovery & Downtime Reduction</h1>
      <p>
        Brownson Industrial Consulting helps manufacturers investigate equipment failures,
        identify root causes, and restore reliability through practical maintenance solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="section">
        <h2>The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          A production facility experienced recurring conveyor failures that disrupted product flow,
          caused line stoppages, and created avoidable downtime. Temporary fixes were being made,
          but the root causes had not been fully addressed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <p>
          Brownson Industrial Consulting performed a structured equipment investigation to identify
          mechanical, operational, and maintenance-related failure points.
        </p>

        <div class="bullets">
          <div class="bullet">• Conveyor inspection and component evaluation</div>
          <div class="bullet">• Root cause analysis of repeated stoppages</div>
          <div class="bullet">• Corrective repair recommendations</div>
          <div class="bullet">• Maintenance strategy improvements</div>
          <div class="bullet">• Reliability-focused follow-up actions</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>The Result</h2>
        <p>
          By identifying the real issues and implementing targeted corrective action,
          the facility achieved measurable performance improvements.
        </p>

        <div class="stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <h3>30%</h3>
            <p>Less Downtime</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <h3>Better</h3>
            <p>Equipment Reliability</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <h3>Stronger</h3>
            <p>Maintenance Response</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Why It Matters</h2>
        <p>
          Investigating recurring equipment issues instead of only reacting to failures helps manufacturers
          reduce costly downtime, improve line performance, and protect production output.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <h2>Need Help Solving Equipment Issues?</h2>
      <p>
        Brownson Industrial Consulting provides maintenance consulting, issue investigation,
        and reliability support for industrial operations.
      </p>
      <a href="index.html#contact" class="btn">Request a Consultation</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 Brownson Industrial Consulting<br>
      Wake Forest, North Carolina • 919-671-6198 • info@brownsonconsulting.com
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
